'''Liechtensteiners''' are a [[Germanic peoples|Germanic]]<ref>{{harvnb|Minahan|2000|p=769}}</ref> people native to [[Liechtenstein]].<ref name="Minahan"/><ref name="Waldman,Mason">{{harvnb|Waldman|Mason|2006|p=486}}</ref> There were approximately 34,000 Germanic Liechtensteiners worldwide at the turn of the 21st century.<ref name="Minahan"/>

